<br>
An additional note: there have been some significant changes in MA Special Attacks of late.  I don't have time to go into them here, but Flower of Life now works for all quality levels (and is definitely a MUST HAVE), and BwT is still the special attack of choice for dmg/time.  When missioning and mowing through mobs quickly with a team, 'Snake and Bird' are both viable for shorter encounters.<br>
<br>
Also, Chronita has further expanded on her amazing inits research, and has demonstrated that MA attacks go from 1.25/1.25 to 1.45/1.45 (iirc) as your MA skill increases to 1000.  So the age old &quot;150 Phys Init is all you need at full agg&quot; should be modified slightly, since you really need closer to 300 if your MA skill is ~1000.<br>
<br>
